node.title: All the COVID news you need from across Australia
node.description: Queensland authorities say the state's first community case in more than a week is considered very low risk, but the southern border town of Goondiwindi is on alert. Follow live.
node.content: ["Queensland authorities say the state's first community case in more than a week is considered very low risk, but the southern border town of Goondiwindi is on alert. Follow live.", "Follow all of Thursday's COVID-19 news and updates on our live blog."]
